; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/linux/diffimg.md

% diffimg, linux

# Calculate the intersection between images and output an image where each pixel is the difference between corresponding pixels in input images
diffimg <path_to_input_image1_ext> <path_to_input_image2_ext> <path_to_output_image_ext>
